description: 2 no. rooflights to both sides of the existing roofslopes. Single storey front extension; conversion of garage into habitable room and replacement of garage door with masonry wall with windows. Alterations to fenestration including enlargements of existing doors, new door and window openings, replacement windows and doors, cill heights of rear ground floor windows lowered and insertion of staircase window to front and rear elevation. New rooflight above ground floor rear breakfast room. New flat glazed roof above front door. [AMENDED DESCRIPTION]
